data.meta_description: Excel Practice - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document contains information about Olympic athletes including their name, gender, city and year of the Olympics, the sport and discipline, and the event. It includes data from several Summer Olympics between 1976 and 2008 featuring athletes from various countries that competed in sports such as swimming, cycling, volleyball, and more. The data showcases gold medalists and their achievements across multiple Olympic games.
